cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "pancData3: Pancreatic DWI Analysis Pipeline"
message: "If you use this software in your research, please cite it as below."
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: Karlin
    given-names: Avery
    affiliation: Memorial Sloan Kettering Cancer Center
repository-code: "https://github.com/akarlin3/pancData3"
license: AGPL-3.0
version: "2.3.1"
date-released: "2026-03-29"
keywords:
  - diffusion-weighted imaging
  - IVIM
  - ADC
  - pancreatic cancer
  - radiotherapy
  - medical physics
  - MRI
  - deep learning denoising
  - survival analysis
abstract: >-
  A MATLAB-based analysis pipeline for pancreatic
  diffusion-weighted MRI research. Supports IVIM and ADC
  model fitting, deep learning denoising (DnCNN, IVIMnet),
  radiotherapy dose correlation, and survival analysis with
  competing risks modeling.
